    "en": {
      "title": "The station master's strike is over",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Railway Department said that the station masters agreed to suspend the industrial action which started at 6.00 pm yesterday (23) by withdrawing from issuing tickets.",
        "This decision was reached in the discussion that ended a few moments ago with the participation of the Secretary of the Ministry of Transport of the Railway General Manager's Office at the Maradana Railway Headquarters."
      ],
